316
00:21:27.640 --> 00:21:29.880
Look. I've been saying hi.

317
00:21:32.050 --> 00:21:33.110
Do you feel sick?

318
00:21:36.449 --> 00:21:38.419
Okay. Let's go in.

319
00:21:50.659 --> 00:21:51.669
Snap out of it.

320
00:22:05.709 --> 00:22:09.350
"Signals that are 100 percent effective."

321
00:22:09.350 --> 00:22:10.979
(Rest your head on his shoulder and tilt it 45 degrees)

322
00:22:10.979 --> 00:22:14.050
"Rest your head on his shoulder and tilt it 45 degrees."

323
00:22:14.590 --> 00:22:17.989
"Pucker your lips toward his face."

324
00:22:22.959 --> 00:22:25.030
