327
00:22:33.269 --> 00:22:34.939
We should look at it thoroughly.

328
00:22:39.449 --> 00:22:41.080
I think we can just take it.

329
00:22:41.949 --> 00:22:44.019
Right? We can just take it.

330
00:22:50.259 --> 00:22:51.590
I'm sleepy.

331
00:22:57.830 --> 00:22:59.030
You're sleepy?

332
00:23:00.169 --> 00:23:01.199
