343
00:23:53.719 --> 00:23:55.320
This is Cucci, not Gucci.

344
00:23:57.489 --> 00:23:58.560
Do you not like it?

345
00:24:03.560 --> 00:24:05.469
Can't you tell what my style is?

346
00:24:08.600 --> 00:24:11.769
They had Brada too. I should've gotten those.

347
00:24:12.239 --> 00:24:15.880
You really are amazing, Mr. Choi Kang.

348
00:24:17.179 --> 00:24:18.479
You're too kind.

349
00:24:18.709 --> 00:24:20.650
Wear these for now.

350
00:24:20.650 --> 00:24:23.949
