353
00:24:31.860 --> 00:24:33.729
I'm happy with these.

354
00:24:35.459 --> 00:24:36.530
Do you mean it?

355
00:24:39.169 --> 00:24:42.070
These are very durable.

356
00:24:42.169 --> 00:24:43.370
Stop talking.

357
00:24:49.880 --> 00:24:51.479
