358
00:24:53.209 --> 00:24:54.550
I make even these look good.

359
00:24:54.749 --> 00:24:58.749
I guess designer goods make the person look classy.

360
00:24:59.050 --> 00:25:00.719
They look great on you.

361
00:25:01.090 --> 00:25:03.090
Wear them for a long, long time. I'll go now.

362
00:25:04.419 --> 00:25:05.459
Have a nice day.

363
00:25:06.459 --> 00:25:07.489
A long, long time.

364
00:25:09.530 --> 00:25:11.429
What is he yapping about after buying me knock-offs?

365
00:25:12.169 --> 00:25:15.699
My gosh. How cheap. They're not Gucci, they're Gucheap.

366
00:25:18.939 --> 00:25:21.140
These are so nice.

367
00:25:21.840 --> 00:25:23.409
It's like they were made for me.

368
00:25:27.209 --> 00:25:28.880
Are you doing the shoot?

369
00:25:29.179 --> 00:25:31.080
