370
00:25:31.479 --> 00:25:32.550
I did not.

371
00:25:32.790 --> 00:25:35.150
This project receives attention nationwide,

372
00:25:35.419 --> 00:25:37.659
so it'll be good for your career as well.

373
00:25:38.759 --> 00:25:41.790
You sound so sweet. Is it because you slept so well?

374
00:25:42.199 --> 00:25:44.560
I did not sleep well.

375
00:25:44.959 --> 00:25:47.900
I worked hard on this series. I wish you'd keep working on it.

376
00:25:51.269 --> 00:25:52.340
No.

377
00:25:52.909 --> 00:25:55.979
Once his files come out, I hope you stick to this project with Soo Chul.

378
00:25:56.939 --> 00:25:58.009
Okay.

379
00:25:58.239 --> 00:25:59.310
Get in.

380
00:26:04.550 --> 00:26:05.590
Hello.

381
00:26:06.850 --> 00:26:07.850
- Hello. - Hello.

382
00:26:08.390 --> 00:26:09.620
How do you feel?

383
00:26:10.419 --> 00:26:12.259
I thought I'd be okay since it's our second,

384
00:26:13.229 --> 00:26:14.530
but I'm twice as nervous.

385
00:26:14.729 --> 00:26:16.159
I can totally understand.

386
00:26:16.929 --> 00:26:18.729
- Come in. - Okay.

387
00:26:18.729 --> 00:26:20.100
Okay.

388
00:26:20.469 --> 00:26:23.499
We'll film the consultation...

389
00:26:23.499 --> 00:26:26.469
as well as the steps afterward.

390
00:26:26.469 --> 00:26:28.269
(Fertility Clinic)

391
00:26:34.280 --> 00:26:35.280
Hello.

392
00:26:37.449 --> 00:26:38.519
Okay.

393
00:26:38.689 --> 00:26:41.959
You've done it before, so you know you need to relax, right?

394
00:26:42.189 --> 00:26:43.219
Yes.

395
00:26:43.659 --> 00:26:45.989
Many people get fertility treatments,

396
00:26:46.259 --> 00:26:48.600
so don't think it's only you.

397
00:26:48.929 --> 00:26:51.429
Think of it as a special way to meet your child.

398
00:26:52.169 --> 00:26:53.169
Okay.

399
00:26:53.530 --> 00:26:54.900
Do you have any questions?

400
00:26:55.100 --> 00:26:57.499
Are there any medications she should avoid?

401
00:26:58.169 --> 00:26:59.840
Vitamins are fine.

402
00:26:59.840 --> 00:27:03.340
You have to consult me first before taking anything else.

403
00:27:03.540 --> 00:27:04.640
Are you taking anything now?

404
00:27:05.550 --> 00:27:07.679
I'm only taking lactobacillus at the moment.

405
00:27:08.209 --> 00:27:09.219
That's fine.

406
00:27:37.080 --> 00:27:38.650
Give her a lot of help.

407
00:27:38.979 --> 00:27:40.050
I will.

408
00:27:40.179 --> 00:27:42.650
Please tell me if there's anything I should do for her.

409
00:27:42.949 --> 00:27:44.080
Just be supportive.

410
00:27:50.860 --> 00:27:54.090
I really hope it works this time.

411
00:27:55.189 --> 00:27:58.459
Must they work so hard and force it?

412
00:28:00.729 --> 00:28:02.469
You have to sacrifice so much...

413
00:28:04.169 --> 00:28:06.310
for a being that doesn't exist.

414
00:28:14.580 --> 00:28:15.620
Look over there.

415
00:28:22.189 --> 00:28:24.620
How could they make a face like that?

416
00:28:27.929 --> 00:28:30.300
When you look at a mom looking at her baby,

417
00:28:31.860 --> 00:28:33.530
isn't it amazing?

418
00:28:34.600 --> 00:28:36.600
Just how must a person love another person...

419
00:28:37.439 --> 00:28:39.110
to make a face like that?

420
00:28:41.070 --> 00:28:42.640
How can a person...

421
00:28:43.580 --> 00:28:45.550
give another person unconditional love...

422
00:28:47.949 --> 00:28:50.650
without wanting anything in return?

423
00:28:56.860 --> 00:28:59.560
I feel like having someone to love like that in itself...

424
00:29:00.130 --> 00:29:02.699
would set me free from being lonely.

425
00:29:05.030 --> 00:29:07.800
Is that why women always choose the baby...

426
00:29:08.669 --> 00:29:10.640
if they had to choose...

427
00:29:11.199 --> 00:29:14.640
between the person they love or their baby?

428
00:29:20.650 --> 00:29:21.650
I won't let go...

429
00:29:23.949 --> 00:29:24.979
of the person I love.

430
00:29:26.919 --> 00:29:29.060
I know that having a baby is a miracle.

431
00:29:31.189 --> 00:29:34.429
But I haven't fallen in love for the past 10 years,

432
00:29:35.630 --> 00:29:38.100
so love is also a miracle to me.

433
00:29:47.310 --> 00:29:49.439
I brought you some popular baby stuff...

434
00:29:49.439 --> 00:29:51.679
for you and Do Ah.

435
00:29:53.310 --> 00:29:55.749
Babies have sensitive skin, so it's important to wash them...

436
00:29:55.749 --> 00:29:57.120
with filtered and clean water.

437
00:29:57.679 --> 00:29:59.290
You're also starting a new life,

438
00:29:59.290 --> 00:30:01.090
so wash yourself properly and become a new person.

439
00:30:02.360 --> 00:30:03.489
Use it well.

440
00:30:04.090 --> 00:30:05.989
And you just need to take a photo to prove that you're using it well.

441
00:30:06.229 --> 00:30:09.360
No, I don't feel any sincerity in what you're saying right now.

442
00:30:10.300 --> 00:30:13.769
You'll realize that I'm sincere once you see all the baby stuff...

443
00:30:13.769 --> 00:30:15.469
that I'll be bringing from now on.

444
00:30:15.840 --> 00:30:17.570
Really? Then let me see that.

445
00:30:35.613 --> 00:30:36.613
What are you doing?

446
00:30:41.824 --> 00:30:44.254
Why aren't you giving it to me? All I did was grab it.

447
00:30:44.254 --> 00:30:45.663
Look how hard you're holding onto it.

448
00:30:45.663 --> 00:30:47.564
Fine. Let's just stay like this all night.

449
00:30:47.564 --> 00:30:48.863
I just changed the showerhead.

450
00:30:50.163 --> 00:30:51.294
And I did it in one go.

451
00:30:52.334 --> 00:30:53.334
I see.

452
00:30:53.804 --> 00:30:56.873
You're turning 40 soon, but you're still so tiny.

453
00:30:56.873 --> 00:30:59.504
I can hug you with just one arm. What's the matter with you?

454
00:30:59.504 --> 00:31:01.403
You should exercise your shoulders and increase your strength.

455
00:31:01.403 --> 00:31:03.544
What do you want? Do you want me to beat you up?

456
00:31:03.774 --> 00:31:05.683
How about I beat you up tonight?

457
00:31:06.014 --> 00:31:07.943
Do Ah, it's time for a bath.

458
00:31:09.984 --> 00:31:10.984
It's warm, isn't it?

459
00:31:13.324 --> 00:31:14.584
My sweetheart.

460
00:31:14.754 --> 00:31:16.754
What are you doing? What's with your face?

461
00:31:17.254 --> 00:31:20.064
I'm trying to look natural as I wash my kid.

462
00:31:20.264 --> 00:31:22.163
Just be yourself. Don't look at the camera.

463
00:31:22.464 --> 00:31:23.534
Do Ah, cover your ears.

464
00:31:25.534 --> 00:31:29.034
I never washed her with her mom, so this is new to me.

465
00:31:30.274 --> 00:31:31.603
I'm just saying.

466
00:31:32.443 --> 00:31:34.343
I was just talking about the situation.

467
00:31:35.004 --> 00:31:37.413
It was just the theme of the shoot.

468
00:31:39.814 --> 00:31:40.843
I'm done taking photos.

469
00:31:44.953 --> 00:31:47.883
I may not be her mom,

470
00:31:48.123 --> 00:31:50.193
but I take care of her like an aunt.

471
00:31:50.294 --> 00:31:52.524
Actually, that's what I am. I'm her aunt.

472
00:31:52.764 --> 00:31:55.363
You're not her aunt. You're just a stranger.

473
00:31:55.593 --> 00:31:57.334
My gosh, don't be so coldhearted.

474
00:31:57.764 --> 00:31:59.433
We're not strangers.

475
00:31:59.433 --> 00:32:00.504
Then what are we?

476
00:32:01.663 --> 00:32:04.633
We're not a family. We're not married.

477
00:32:05.234 --> 00:32:06.873
We're pretty much a family.

478
00:32:06.873 --> 00:32:08.173
Right, Do Ah?

479
00:32:13.814 --> 00:32:16.453
Come here and help me wash her. Hurry up and sit down.

480
00:32:16.784 --> 00:32:18.613
Here. You told me this is good.

481
00:32:19.653 --> 00:32:21.254
(Bareun Hospital)

482
00:32:24.054 --> 00:32:25.224
(The Baby Jang Ha Ri)

483
00:32:34.334 --> 00:32:36.474
- Hello, Ms. Shim. - Hey, Ha Ri.

484
00:32:37.203 --> 00:32:39.173
The babysitter called and said she can't make it today,

485
00:32:39.173 --> 00:32:41.343
so I have to stay with my baby today.

486
00:32:42.103 --> 00:32:43.244
Is your baby okay?

487
00:32:43.673 --> 00:32:46.544
She just needs to take a few tests at the hospital.

488
00:32:47.343 --> 00:32:49.214
Tell them that I'll send them the report soon.

489
00:32:49.653 --> 00:32:51.853
Can you just check the manuscript that needs to be sent today?

490
00:32:52.254 --> 00:32:53.324
Okay, sure.

491
00:32:55.484 --> 00:32:56.554
Oh, dear.

492
00:33:03.363 --> 00:33:05.494
Hey, Jae Yi.

493
00:33:05.964 --> 00:33:07.703
It's okay. I'll hold you.

494
00:33:08.133 --> 00:33:09.903
There, there.

495
00:33:10.574 --> 00:33:14.074
Just a second. I need to get some work done.

496
00:33:14.074 --> 00:33:15.504
(The Baby Booklet Plan: May, Children's Day)

497
00:33:15.504 --> 00:33:16.574
It's okay.

498
00:33:19.244 --> 00:33:21.343
(Do Yeon's Daycare Center)

499
00:33:22.413 --> 00:33:24.084
Hello, ma'am.

500
00:33:25.784 --> 00:33:28.853
Did I not pack Do Yeon's blanket?

501
00:33:29.893 --> 00:33:32.863
I'm sorry. Right now, I'm with her sister at the hospital.

502
00:33:34.923 --> 00:33:37.564
What should I do? There's no one I can send to fetch her blanket.

503
00:33:40.133 --> 00:33:42.303
Yes, can you just cover her with that?

504
00:33:43.174 --> 00:33:46.243
Okay, thank you. Bye.

505
00:33:48.274 --> 00:33:49.573
Jae Yi.

506
00:33:51.614 --> 00:33:53.013
It's okay.

507
00:33:55.044 --> 00:33:56.584
I can do this alone.

508
00:33:57.353 --> 00:33:58.683
We're at the hospital.

509
00:33:59.524 --> 00:34:00.584
You're okay now.

510
00:34:17.134 --> 00:34:18.203
Ms. Shim.

511
00:34:23.013 --> 00:34:25.413
